        <item>
            <title>Insta360 Ace Pro 2 疑中國下架，香港用家：對起霧極失望 + 應一早回收</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/insta360-ace-pro-2/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=insta360-ace-pro-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/insta360-ace-pro-2/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 07:00:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insta360]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insta360 Ace Pro 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275886</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">上月開賣的運動攝影機 Insta360 Ace Pro 2，被大量用家發現起霧問題，更有人揚言會轉會至其他品牌，有網民指已知會客服但未獲回覆。中國各地暫時官方網店已全線「缺貨」，疑似被下架；惟香港官方網店仍然有得賣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275890 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241118at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有用家上傳影片，指 Insta360 Ace Pro 2 出現起霧問題（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q_B7EieMU6o">中年流浪貓 / ㄓˋㄩˋ</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">可以拍攝 8K 30fps 解像度影片及具備雙 AI 晶片的 Insta360 Ace Pro 2，被網民發現有起霧問題。有網民在 Insta360 用家的 Facebook 羣組內發文表示：「警世！救得一個得一個！Insta Ace pro 2 完全為失敗之作！想買未買，唔好曬錢！！！」，並指推出至今，Insta360 都未有解決 Ace Pro 2 發熱起霧問題，亦未有回收方案，客服一直迴避問題，因此極度失望。有網民留言表示，趁有優惠價買 Ace Pro 1 比買 Ace Pro 2 更好，更指對 Ace Pro 2 沒有信心，應一早回收。有網民指會轉會至 DJI，更有人笑稱 Ace Pro 2 像時光倒流 10 年前的 gopro，都有發熱起霧問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275891 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-694x227.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-694x227.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民指：「Insta Ace pro 2 完全為失敗之作！想買未買，唔好曬錢！！！」（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275892 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民留言表示，趁有優惠價買 Ace Pro 1 比買 Ace Pro 2 更好（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275894 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3-694x262.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="262" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3-694x262.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-3.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民留言表示 Ace Pro 2 應一早回收（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bsgq1Amg1&amp;share_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2F17qqiuzRYm%2F">Insta360 Hong Kong User Group</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275893 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2-694x380.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="380" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2-694x380.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241118_-2.jpg 1128w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民指會轉會至 DJI（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/insta360hk/permalink/2626872570833114/?rdid=tWogXf9Bs